Headers: DocuSign Could Bounce Before Another Downside Test
Description: In an "Executive Decision" segment of Mad Money Wednesday evening, Jim Cramer spoke with Dan Springer, CEO of DocuSign Inc.  .  DocuSign reported a magnificent quarter at the beginning of the month, Cramer said.  At least in the way it pertains to DocuSign's business.
